title: Yong Indochina Suppenbar
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Tiny place offering a small Vietnamese food menu with tofu option for the coconut curry soup, bo bun noodle and vegetable salad with ginger dressing, and spring roll-like baguettes (options made vegan on request). Because rice noodle is used, everything is gluten-free. There are also a number of fresh juices, including a fresh limeade made with cane sugar and a ginger and lemon juice drink.
